&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-style: italic;"&gt;Let’s be honest about what happened this week: the United States didn’t end a war with Iran. It bought two weeks of slightly reduced chaos, declared victory, and hoped nobody would read the fine print. They should read the fine print.&lt;/p&gt;
